1386JSC::IsoSubspace* JSRTCPeerConnection::subspaceForImpl(JSC::VM& vm)
1387{
1388 auto& clientData = *static_cast<JSVMClientData*>(vm.clientData);
1389 auto& spaces = clientData.subspaces();
1390 if (auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForRTCPeerConnection.get())
1391 return space;
1392 static_assert(std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSRTCPeerConnection> || !JSRTCPeerConnection::needsDestruction);
1393 if constexpr (std::is_base_of_v<JSC::JSDestructibleObject, JSRTCPeerConnection>)
1394 spaces.m_subspaceForRTCPeerConnection = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.destructibleObjectHeapCellType.get(), JSRTCPeerConnection);
1395 else
1396 spaces.m_subspaceForRTCPeerConnection = makeUnique<IsoSubspace> ISO_SUBSPACE_INIT(vm.heap, vm.cellHeapCellType.get(), JSRTCPeerConnection);
1397 auto* space = spaces.m_subspaceForRTCPeerConnection.get();
1398IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("unreachable-code")
1399IGNORE_WARNINGS_BEGIN("tautological-compare")
1400 void (*myVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSRTCPeerConnection::visitOutputConstraints;
1401 void (*jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)(JSC::JSCell*, JSC::SlotVisitor&) = JSC::JSCell::visitOutputConstraints;
1402 if (myVisitOutputConstraint != jsCellVisitOutputConstraint)
1403 clientData.outputConstraintSpaces().append(space);
1404IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1405IGNORE_WARNINGS_END
1406 return space;
1407}

1418bool JSRTCPeerConnectionOwner::isReachableFromOpaqueRoots(JSC::Handle<JSC::Unknown> handle, void*, AbstractSlotVisitor& visitor, const char** reason)
1419{
1420 auto* jsRTCPeerConnection = jsCast<JSRTCPeerConnection*>(handle.slot()->asCell());
1421 auto& wrapped = jsRTCPeerConnection->wrapped();
1422 if (!wrapped.isContextStopped() && wrapped.hasPendingActivity()) {
1423 if (UNLIKELY(reason))
1424 *reason = "ActiveDOMObject with pending activity";
1425 return true;
1426 }
1427 if (jsRTCPeerConnection->wrapped().isFiringEventListeners()) {
1428 if (UNLIKELY(reason))
1429 *reason = "EventTarget firing event listeners";
1430 return true;
1431 }
1432 UNUSED_PARAM(visitor);
1433 UNUSED_PARAM(reason);
1434 return false;
1435}

1463

1467

1470 // to toJS() we currently require RTCPeerConnection you to opt out of binding hardening
1471 // by adding the SkipVTableValidation attribute to the interface IDL definition
1472 RELEASE_ASSERT(actualVTablePointer == expectedVTablePointer);
1473#endif
